/**
 * Requests that the animation be played, starting on the next frame. If the animation is complete, it restarts from the beginning.

 * @alias ani.run
 * @namespace ani.play
 */
description: Requests that the animation be played, starting on the next frame. If the animation is complete, it restarts from the beginning.
name: play

comment:

name: playing

description: Apply the animation at its current progress.
name: apply

comment:
